tafsir[2]{c,v,t}:
  21,50,"Ndee Alqur'aanaare Jippinaande e Muhammadu (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna) ko nde waaju wonannde on faalaaɗo waajitornde nde heewunde nafa e moƴƴere. Kaa hara onon on yedday nde wonndude ɗum? Hara on qirritaaki ko woni kon e mayre on gollirtaa nde?"
  21,54,"Ibraahiima Maakani ɓe: \"Gomɗii on wonii -onon jokkuɓe ɓen- e baabiraaɓe mo'on sincuɓe ɓen e nder majjere ɓanngunde gaayi Laawol Goongo ngol."